# DRY / reuse (mandatory)

Never copy-paste.

- **Repeated value → named const.** Extract to `frontend/src/config/constants.ts` or a
  co-located `*.consts.ts`, then import everywhere.
- **Repeated logic → shared function.** Pure helpers in `frontend/src/utils/`; React state/effects
  in `frontend/src/hooks/`. Never duplicate the body.
- **Rule of three.** Before a value/expression/JSX shell lands on a **third** site, extract the
  shared const/util/hook/component first.
- **Reuse before create.** Search existing utils/hooks/components before adding new ones.

Reference: `frontend/src/utils/`, `frontend/src/hooks/`, `frontend/src/components/common/`.
